{"tid":1234756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】絕食反惡法　教大講師黎明堅持近 90 小時後不適送院","createTime":"2019-06-17T03:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T03:54:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55445e31270fddc694a04e3413ce214d953c0359","tid":1234756,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/114930_7adea785a30f5b5907fdeab3665e69d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F114930_7adea785a30f5b5907fdeab3665e69d6.png&h=919cfe3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名藝文界人士在周三起於立法會大樓附近絕食，反對《逃犯條例》修訂。其中絕食近 90 小時香港教育大學講師黎明，今午因不適送院。行動目標是在明日早上 7 點完結，屆時部份人絕食時間長達 103 小時，象徵早前 103 萬名市民上街反惡法。<br />\n<br />\n多名藝文及學界人士，包括楊慧儀、莫昭如、應亮、何式凝、黎明，陳曉蕾，三木，邱偉平，陳燕遐，蔡金銓，康展華等，在 6 月12 日凌晨零時零分開始，絕食 48 至 91 小時不等，爭取撤回《逃犯條例》修訂。<br />\n<br />\n「性/別公義委員會」FB專頁在今日下午1時許透露，絕食者當中有些血壓偏高，有些血糖過低。而黎明情況比較差，血糖低至1.9，亦有發燒及腳步不穩。在醫護人員照料下，躺在陰涼處休息了一會兒。至今午黎明因不適需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n政府在下午宣布暫緩修例工作，但「絕食明志反惡法」隨即發聲明，表明不接受僅暫緩修例，要求政府立即撤回修例，釋放被捕示威者及不得秋後算帳，並要求林鄭問責下台。<br />\n<br />\n他們又表明，會繼續完成103小時的絕食行動，象徵103萬人上街反惡法。他們指雖然103小時的絕食明早結束，「但他日政府敢再重提惡法，我們必定再回來」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/反送中-絕食反惡法-教大講師黎明堅持近-90-小時後不適送院/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%83%A1%E6%B3%95-%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%E8%AC%9B%E5%B8%AB%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E8%BF%91-90-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%2F&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWrzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=091071b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%83%A1%E6%B3%95-%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%E8%AC%9B%E5%B8%AB%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E8%BF%91-90-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%2F&h=b6ea4a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/反送中-絕食反惡法-教大講師黎明堅持近-90-小時後不適送院/</a>"},{"pid":"c43d7c02fefc69ef1acd7e4852d95669b600c83f","tid":1234756,"uid":134268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea37189c53e2daa09fee759f215a7a7b390a44a","tid":1234756,"uid":148987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kfXQFF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kfXQFF.png&h=9a1ff03a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"942c41b3d1c777db3112e4741bf24a563fb93b56","tid":1234756,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cad312328e198991172a4362d5ff26dff0221d","tid":1234756,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64579411_10161850314895082_528231830097231872_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQlo4VUbyKEEG0oeCjDt3u83gCzMl9ZDPB0i71HvzR8Hic4spr7r7wCzWHvYS4b9VOI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=66b81ac0f5b2d0894c60d6f974d873c3&amp;oe=5D937F2C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64579411_10161850314895082_528231830097231872_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQlo4VUbyKEEG0oeCjDt3u83gCzMl9ZDPB0i71HvzR8Hic4spr7r7wCzWHvYS4b9VOI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D66b81ac0f5b2d0894c60d6f974d873c3%26oe%3D5D937F2C&h=53686159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10161850314870082&amp;set=a.10153077343520082&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10161850314870082%26set%3Da.10153077343520082%26type%3D3%26theater&d=4IeB